{"tid":300534,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動畫銀魂吉田松陽CV山寺宏一・將於銀魂電影真人版扮演吉田松陽","createTime":"2017-06-28T03:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T14:03:10.000Z","uid":19232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34733a1760964921a7b37978693258485918933b","tid":300534,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:52:19.000Z","msg":"声優の山寺宏一が、小栗旬主演で空知英秋氏の人気漫画を実写化する映画『銀魂』（7月14日公開）に出演していることがわかった<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2093191/full/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oricon.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2093191%2Ffull%2F&d=u1%2FEs3OS3SrFj2rHSft%2FFdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b774af57\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2093191/full/</a><br />\n物語のキーパーソンとなる吉田松陽の声を務める<br />\n<br />\n普段はやる気なし、下品でいつもぐうたらしている銀時だが、実はかつて攘夷戦争で恐れられた伝説の侍。幕府指名手配中の攘夷志士の生き残り・桂小太郎（岡田将生）と攘夷過激派武装集団&ldquo;鬼兵隊&rdquo;の頭領・高杉晋助（堂本剛）とは、攘夷戦争時代の盟友で、松陽が開いていた&ldquo;松下村塾&rdquo;にて共に武士道を学んだ幼なじみだった。激しき攘夷戦争を経て、松陽を失い道を違えた3人。銀時は腰の刀を木刀に持ち替え、新八、神楽と今は騒がしくも呑気な日々を送っている。"},{"pid":"9b5caa27f78ca558510448679ee17f50374306ef","tid":300534,"uid":11913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a60147eb8424957fd7b857ecdd5e6ceb69646f6","tid":300534,"uid":51058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4af523eeb0461cfcd417de6e96d6a1ae945535","tid":300534,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"松陽後生靚仔樣喎"},{"pid":"86fe5aad0392c6d80b0d279240c73b6c9b7db898","tid":300534,"uid":19232,